data.description: Awesome totally remodeled home in northwest Omaha in a nice and quiet neighborhood. New flooring and painting throughout the house, new water heather, recent installed furnace and roof, walk out basement leading to a nice, big, flat back yard to enjoy gatherings with relatives and friends. This gem also has a second kitchen at the basement which can be used as a bar if desired. Both kitchen have granite countertops. two refrigerators and two range/ovens are included in the sale. Also the basement has one bedroom & one flex room. The property also includes a two car garage and a driveway where another six cars can be parked off street.  Call to set up a showing of this fantastic home. A.M.A.
